
= Gift Economy Network

URL = https://www.hearth.net/
=Description=

"The idea of a network for sharing gifts first came to Libor Malý in 2008 at the start of the global economic crisis.

We had many questions at the beginning, including: “How should we name a place where people are living in cooperation?” While seeking the answer, two words came up – “Heart” and “Earth”. Both share the same root. And when you merge them, you get Hearth.

So we found a symbol of the values that are important to us and that we want to advance. 

Hearth.net started on the Internet, but we aim to go further. It is our online tool to improve the gift economy in the real world. With its help we want to create genuine connections, relationships and communities and have fun doing it. And with you too."
(https://www.hearth.net/en/#subpage-about)

